summary: An experienced Product Manager with several years experience, managing all aspects of the product lifecycle including concepting, sourcing, Retail, planning, design, marketing, delivery and launch. A proven track record of delivering on complex multi-product categories for both online and offline channels with a high degree of commerciality within large companies. With a keen eye for detail an understanding of footwear and accessoires and manufacturing processes, I am able to apply these skills effectively across multiple product categories resulting in strong product ranges for customers
